               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150215-80-cd478" type="crimeDate">18th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-80-off477 t18150215-80-cd478"></join>, one feather-bed, value 3 l. one bolster, value 10 s. and two blankets. value 10 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18150215-80-victim684" type="victimName">
                        Lohens 
                        Opperman
                     <interp inst="t18150215-80-victim684" type="surname" value="Opperman"></interp>
